text: Aleksandar Fabijanić (born 18 June 1965) is a Croatian rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Croatia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rijeka
